text: Göcek Tüneli () is a road tunnel in Dalaman, Muğla. The tunnel goes through D400 road. It takes its name from Göcek. It was opened on 9 September 2006, by the president of the term Recep Tayyip Erdoğan. ==References== Category:Road tunnels in Turkey Category:Fethiye District Category:Tunnels in Turkey
title: Göcek Tunnel
